{
  "stem": "24130.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I said, when they took away my-- my cous-- from-- my mother's cousins, to Poland, the next day they came and they opened up the doors, and they took out the furniture and the clothes and everything.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were just standing and watching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And they said, now we could go already to their homes and take it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I didn't even want to hear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't want to look at nobody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[SOBBING] We were just so depressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was already glad that we 're leaving the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we left the town and we came to-- to this Irsava.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First we-- we came to this-- it was a big synagogue there in Irsava.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they put us down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there they said-- like they put, in one house, they took a few streets they-- and they said that this is the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't figure out what a ghetto looks like.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I found out that a few streets, they made it into a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they put us-- we were-- my mother had two sisters, like I said.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The two sisters had-- one had five children, one had six children, and we were five.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I forgot all about to tell you how my-- my sister already came to America after my mother died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I go back to this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When my mother died, my father says, there's nothing for us here anymore and we're going to immigrate to America.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had family here and he-- he wrote my mother's cousin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wrote to my mother's cousin that my mother died, and he's left with six children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says he would like to come to America if she could send us papers to America.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
